<div id="v230.133.2"><span class="H2896 s"><i>It is</i> like the precious</span><span class="H8081 s"> ointment</span><span class="H7218 s"> upon the head</span><span class="H3381 s">, that ran down</span><span class="H2206 s"> upon the beard</span><span class="H175 s">, <i>even</i> Aaron's</span><span class="H2206 s"> beard</span><span class="H3381 s">: that went down</span><span class="H6310 s"> to the skirts</span><span class="H4060 s"> of his garments</span>;</div> 
